tion,\nwhere several novel extensions and results are derived, and some new, such as\nthe principal-agent problem, the efficient portfolio problem, a model of a\nconsumer with market power, and a cost-constrained profit maximization model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Oct 2013 22:51:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-29"}
